Insider Activity


Individual




J. Michael Losh



Mr. J. M. Losh is Chairman at Masco Corp., Independent Non-Executive Director at Aon Plc, Independent Director at Prologis, Inc., and Independent Director at H.B. Fuller Co. He is on the Board of Directors at Aon Plc, TRW Automotive Holdings Corp., Prologis, Inc., H.B. Fuller Co., TRW Automotive, Inc., The Detroit Institute of Arts, and Prologis LP.
Mr. Losh was previously employed as Independent Director by CareFusion Corp., Chairman by Metaldyne Corp., a Managing Director by General Motors de Mexico S de RL de CV, Finance Director by General Motors do Brasil Ltda., and Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by General Motors Corp. He also served on the board at AMB Property Corp., H. B. Fuller Ventures, Inc., Cardinal Health, Inc., General Motors Acceptance Corp., Delphi Automotive Systems Corp., Economic Alliance for Michigan, Electronic Data Systems Corp., and The Quaker Oats Co.
He received his undergraduate degree from Kettering University and an MBA from Harvard University.



